Step 1: Download & install Microsoft Monitoring Agent (MMA)
1. Windows 64-bit
https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=828603
2. Linux
https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=692028
Learn more about installation of MMA agent.

Step 2: Download and install dependency agent
1. Windows 64-bit
https://aka.ms/dependencyagentwindows
2. Linux
https://aka.ms/dependencyagentlinux
Learn more about installation of dependency agent.
If you have machines with no internet connectivity to Log Analytics, you need to download and install Log Analytics gateway.

Learn more

Step 3: Configure MMA agent
