Yv9st5kx7cqsJCWAlVy/0ShcyoCu2O65EzjTOoNW7F+mGrpgsXd3rN7IaS2lhWKo0494SFmS0R6kKGu/WyjI6A==


-  Instalar cliente de MMA e Dependecy nos servidores Linux com os comandos abaixo:
	Acessar o servidor via ssh:
ssh demouser@192.168.0.8

	Elevar o privilégio do usuário:
sudo -s

	Baixar o cliente de MMA (add os dados de workspace id e key):
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Microsoft/OMS-Agent-for-Linux/master/installer/scripts/onboard_agent.sh && sh onboard_agent.sh -w 72485433-2128-48cd-bfe4-4cf4784f146a -s Yv9st5kx7cqsJCWAlVy/0ShcyoCu2O65EzjTOoNW7F+mGrpgsXd3rN7IaS2lhWKo0494SFmS0R6kKGu/WyjI6A==

	Reiniciar o cliente MMA:
/opt/microsoft/omsagent/bin/service_control restart 72485433-2128-48cd-bfe4-4cf4784f146a

	Baixar o client do dendency:
wget --content-disposition https://aka.ms/dependencyagentlinux -O InstallDependencyAgent-Linux64.bin

	Instalar o client do dendency:
sh InstallDependencyAgent-Linux64.bin -s

chmod +x InstallDependencyAgent-Linux64.bin ./InstallDependencyAgent-Linux64.bin --extract